feedbacks.title: Michelle Gobeil
feedbacks.description: I came by some of your work online and love it! The reason I'm contacting you is that I need a logo for my personal brand and was wondering if you could help me out with that. I don't have a very high budget so I would prefer it if you don't spend too much time on it.

feedbacks.title: Gobeil
feedbacks.description: I'm an children's book illustrator and I need a logo of my own name for my website, social media and possibly to be used on my books. What I would like is my name, Michelle Gobeil, displayed like it was written with a pencil or brush or anything like that. It would be perfect if you could create the logo without using a font because I would like it to be unique.
